@@TJvCustomSpeedButton.DropDownMenu
Summary
  Identifies a pop-up menu associated with the speed button.
Description
  Assign a value to DropDownMenu to make a menu appear when the button is pressed. (To display the
  menu programmatically, call the speed button’s Click or ButtonClickmethod.) If the menu’s AutoPopup
  property is set to true, the menu appears automatically. If AutoPopup is false, display the menu by
  calling the menu’s Popup method in the speed button’s OnClick event handler.
See Also
  TJvCustomSpeedButton.Click, TJvCustomSpeedButton.MarkDropDown, TJvCustomSpeedButton.MenuPosition

